race.comment: MORIKAWA (2) ran the fastest on the card last time scoring by 4 lengths (19.20) at this track. Expected to go close again. JUST BE BEAR (1) jumped favourite and was too quick with an all-the-way win last start (19.80) at this track in a Grade 6 over 340m. Leading player again. OPAL ONYX (4) was a strong winner (16.00) from box 1 last time, scoring by 3 lengths at Launceston. Has the squeeze box to overcome and will need the breaks early. Winner at her latest appearance in one of the quickest times on the card. One of the key runners again. ELKO (7) scored by 1.5 lengths last time (16.16) in a Restricted WIN over 278m at Launceston. Has two wins already from this draw.
